                                                                            <comments>
                            <comment id="68606" author="rhenwood" created="Tue, 8 Oct 2013 17:39:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve taken this request to the Docbook mailing list. This functionality is not support at this time.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="66955" author="rhenwood" created="Wed, 18 Sep 2013 19:12:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It looks to me from a quick search that the switch to provide this behavoir is described here:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://wiki.apache.org/xmlgraphics-fop/ExtensionsForPdf&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://wiki.apache.org/xmlgraphics-fop/ExtensionsForPdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;And there is a proto-type implementation here:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=45390&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=45390&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;However, this doesn&apos;t look like it has landed in the version of Docbook that we are using...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I will follow up on the Docbook mailing list.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
